		  <p><img src="/images/IdaPartySmall.jpg" alt="IDA Party" width="180" height="120" /></p>
		  <p>The IDA project celebrated one year of successful savings in December
		    2007.<br />
		    Savers, project staff, and a representative from the Chicago Major's
		    Office for People with Disabilities attended a ceremony honoring
		    everyone's efforts. Thus far, the group has saved over $7,000 for goals
		    such as post-secondary education, purchase of a condominium, or starting
		    a small business.</p>
		</div>
		
